data.description: Experience luxurious living in this exquisite 6-bedroom, 5-bathroom built by Toll Brothers. With its modern open-concept kitchen, perfect for hosting lively gatherings, and a one-of-a-kind movie theater, this home offers a blend of elegance and entertainment that is truly unmatched. The property boasts a primary bedroom and full bath on the main level, a spacious layout, stunning outdoor space, and exceptional amenities, making it an ideal haven for relaxation and recreation. Situated in the sought-after development of Marlboro Ridge which offers homeowners an opportunity to enjoy a low-maintenance, active lifestyle in a picturesque neighborhood just 20 miles from Washington D.C. in Upper Marlboro. Living at Marlboro Ridge means you’ll enjoy resort style amenities including a clubhouse and pool, extensive walking and hiking trails, playgrounds, a state-of-the-art equestrian center and riding arena and more.  Priced at $1,100,000, this luxurious property is a true gem awaiting its lucky buyer. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity - schedule a viewing today!
